STATEMENT REGARDING RESEARCH UNIX EDITIONS 8, 9, AND 10

Alcatel-Lucent USA Inc. ("ALU-USA"), on behalf of itself and Nokia Bell Laboratories, agrees that it will not assert its copyright rights against the non-commercial copying, distribution, performance, display, or creation of derivative works of Research Unix Editions 8, 9, and 10.

This statement does not:
(i) transfer ownership of, or relinquish any, intellectual property rights (including patent rights) belonging to Nokia Corporation, ALU-USA or any of their affiliates;
(ii) grant a license to any patent, patent application or trademark of Nokia Corporation, ALU-USA or any of their affiliates;
(iii) grant any third-party rights or licenses; or
(iv) grant any rights for commercial purposes.

Neither ALU-USA nor Nokia Bell Laboratories will furnish or provide support for the Research Unix Editions and make no warranties or representations, including that the Research Unix Editions do not infringe third-party intellectual property rights or are fit for any particular purpose.
